    "body" : "<p>Alternatively, you could use <code>@RequiredArgsConstructor</code>. This adds a constructor for all fields that are either <code>@NonNull</code> or <code>final</code>.</p>\n<p>See the <a href=\"https://projectlombok.org/features/constructor\" rel=\"noreferrer\">documentation</a></p>\n"
