  "title" : "Java Lombok: Omitting one field in @AllArgsConstructor?",
  "body" : "<p>If I specify <em>@AllArgsConstructor</em> using <strong>Lombok</strong>, it will generate a constructor for setting all the declared (not final, not static) fields. \nIs it possible to omit some field and this leave generated constructor for all other fields?</p>\n"
}